      "context": "Suburb/postcode search dropdown - Open state with results. Shows 8 max results. Each row: suburb name, state badge (NSW/VIC/QLD/etc), postcode badge, and Zone/Small icon badge indicating the geographic zone. First row is highlighted (hover/selected state). Default empty state variant: Suburb Search / Default (4pkAW). React implementation: use react-query + debounced input to search Australian suburbs API. Zone badge is determined by postcode mapping.",
