    {
      "type": "frame",
      "id": "gbSZC",
      "x": 4105,
      "y": 5393,
      "name": "Visa Date Picker / Input / Filled",
      "context": "Visa Date Picker / Input / Filled — Trigger button that opens the Visa Date Picker calendar (esEoC or KKpmy). Shows label 'Arrival Date in Australia' + calendar icon + selected date value (e.g. '15 Mar 2025'). Below the trigger: a short description, a VEVO hint ('Not sure? Check your exact arrival date on VEVO.'), and a clickable link to https://online.immi.gov.au/evo/firstParty?actionType=query labeled 'Open VEVO — visa details & conditions'. In React: a button wrapping shadcn/ui Popover trigger. When clicked, opens a Popover containing the Calendar component. The filled state means a date has been selected. Companion empty state: gluUE.",
      "reusable": true,
      "width": 280,
      "layout": "vertical",
      "gap": 6,
      "children": [
        {
